div.p:
TWo Comedians acting upon the Stage the parts of Servingmen; one askt the other to go drink, whither ſhall we go ſaid one; the other replyed (eſpying a fellow groping a Wench in the Gallery) let us go to the Hand in Placket; thereupon the fellow ſneakt away his hand; which the other perceiving, cryed out; 

                        •
                     ay friend, if you remove the ſign, we ſhall hardly find the houſe.
